text: haey duong chetd mdeay robsa mou sa vinh klaytowchea tte saat ( min khval avei krawpi mou sa laey) . pitabrakd nasa neang staerte bangheanh brab( anaketiet) ampi rueng mou sa( tha chea kaun robsa neang) tow haey brasenbae yeung( a l laoh) minban tbarommo robsa neang daembi aoy neang sthetnow knongchamnaom anak del mean chomnue te noh
